properties.otherAdvice:

A 24/7 COVID-19 pop-up drive-through clinic is now operating at Brewarrina Multi Purpose Service.

No booking is required.

Delays may be experienced for those queuing for testing.

Visit the NSW Health website for a full list of other testing locations.

properties.headline: SPECIAL EVENT CLEARWAYS - SURRY HILLS Chalmers Street between Cleveland Street AND Devonshire Street
properties.otherAdvice:
Special event clearways will be in effect on both sides of Chalmers St between Cleveland St and Devonshire St to facilitate rail replacement bus operations for Sydney Trains trackwork. 

Clearways are strict no-parking zones and apply even to local residents or RMS Mobility Scheme Permit holders. Check signs before parking as vehicles left in clearways will be towed and a fee applies.
